msgctxt "#31571"
msgid "Highlight a logo from the palette below and click to assign it to DVD and standard-definition video files."
msgstr "Sorot logo daripada palet di bawah dan klik untuk menetapkannya kepada fail video DVD dan definisi standard."

# --- Body texts: left menu category buttons (controls 91–97) ---

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31572"
msgid "View only ultra-high-definition and 4K logo designs in the palette grid."
msgstr "Lihat reka bentuk logo ultra-tinggi dan 4K sahaja dalam grid palet."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31573"
msgid "View only HEVC and H.265 codec logo designs in the palette grid."
msgstr "Lihat reka bentuk logo kodek HEVC dan H.265 sahaja dalam grid palet."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31574"
msgid "View only AVC and H.264 codec logo designs in the palette grid."
msgstr "Lihat reka bentuk logo kodek AVC dan H.264 sahaja dalam grid palet."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31575"
msgid "View only DivX, XviD, and legacy MPEG-4 format logo designs in the palette grid."
msgstr "Lihat reka bentuk logo format DivX, XviD, dan MPEG-4 lama sahaja dalam grid palet."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31576"
msgid "View classic MPEG, DVD, and standard TV broadcast logo designs in the palette grid."
msgstr "Lihat reka bentuk logo MPEG klasik, DVD, dan siaran TV standard sahaja dalam grid palet."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31577"
msgid "View Windows Media Video and VC-1 codec logo designs in the palette grid."
msgstr "Lihat reka bentuk logo kodek Windows Media Video dan VC-1 sahaja dalam grid palet."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31578"
msgid "View container wrappers, disk formats, and other miscellaneous logo designs in the palette grid."
msgstr "Lihat pembalut bekas, format cakera, dan reka bentuk logo pelbagai lain sahaja dalam grid palet."

# --- Standalone entries (no colored prefix) ---

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31579"
msgid "Close this flag customization dialog and return to settings."
msgstr "Tutup dialog penyesuaian bendera ini dan kembali ke tetapan."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31580"
msgid "Highlight any logo design in the center grid and click to save it as your custom flag for the active category."
msgstr "Sorot mana-mana reka bentuk logo dalam grid tengah dan klik untuk menyimpannya sebagai bendera tersuai anda bagi kategori aktif."

# --- Body texts: right panel actions (controls 801, 98) ---

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31581"
msgid "Clear your custom flag choice and restore this category to the skin's automatic default flag logic."
msgstr "Kosongkan pilihan bendera tersuai anda dan pulihkan kategori ini ke logik bendera lalai automatik skin."

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31582"
msgid "Toggle global flag artwork between colored designs and monochromatic default white."
msgstr "Togol seni bendera global antara reka bentuk berwarna dan putih lalai monokromatik."

# --- Default / idle state ---

#: /16x9/includes.xml
msgctxt "#31583"
msgid "Use your directional keys to navigate options. Press Back or select Exit at any time to close without changes."
msgstr "Gunakan kekunci arah anda untuk mengemudi pilihan. Tekan Kembali atau pilih Keluar pada bila-bila masa untuk menutup tanpa perubahan."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31584"
msgid "Select to modify"
msgstr "Pilih untuk mengubah suai"

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31901"
msgid "Customisation of the home screen, widgets and shortcuts menu."
msgstr "Penyesuaian skrin utama, widget dan menu pintasan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31904"
msgid "Script for skinners to let users select an image resource addon."
msgstr "Skrip untuk pembina skin membenarkan pengguna memilih pengaya sumber imej."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31905"
msgid "Automatically adds extra artwork for media in your media libraries."
msgstr "Menambah karya seni tambahan secara automatik untuk media dalam perpustakaan media anda."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31907"
msgid "Lyrics for music. Required to enable animated lyrics."
msgstr "Lirik untuk muzik. Diperlukan untuk mendayakan lirik beranimasi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31908"
msgid "Sync your collection and watched status with trakt.tv."
msgstr "Segerakkan koleksi dan status ditonton anda dengan trakt.tv."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31910"
msgid "Create a custom favourite from selected kodi favourites."
msgstr "Cipta kegemaran tersuai daripada kegemaran kodi terpilih."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31911"
msgid "Edit the home screen menu, widgets, backgrounds and infolines."
msgstr "Edit menu skrin utama, widget, latar belakang dan talian maklumat."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31912"
msgid "Reset the home screen menu, widgets, backgrounds and infolines to default."
msgstr "Tetapkan semula menu skrin utama, widget, latar belakang dan talian maklumat ke lalai."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31913"
msgid "Create a custom favourite from selected kodi favourites. For use in main menu widgets. Requires script favourites to be installed."
msgstr "Cipta kegemaran tersuai daripada kegemaran kodi terpilih. Untuk kegunaan dalam widget menu utama. Memerlukan skrip kegemaran dipasang."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31914"
msgid "Create a custom addon favourite from installed addons. For use in main menu widgets."
msgstr "Cipta pengaya kegemaran tersuai daripada pengaya dipasang. Untuk kegunaan dalam widget menu utama."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31915"
msgid "Reset the skin theme and colours to default."
msgstr "Tetapkan semula tema skin dan warna ke lalai."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31916"
msgid "Select from a list of pre-defined themes."
msgstr "Pilih daripada senarai tema pratakrif."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31917"
msgid "Lock preferences to disable view mode, view options, info dialog and fullscreen settings."
msgstr "Kunci pilihan untuk menyahdayakan mod paparan, pilihan paparan, dialog maklumat dan tetapan skrin penuh."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31918"
msgid "Customise the home screen, favourites, predefined themes and kiosk mode."
msgstr "Sesuaikan skrin utama, kegemaran, tema pratakrif dan mod kios."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31919"
msgid "Change skin theme textures."
msgstr "Tukar tekstur tema skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31920"
msgid "Customise the skin texture colours."
msgstr "Sesuaikan warna tekstur skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31921"
msgid "Customise the background and fallbacks for specific skin areas."
msgstr "Sesuaikan latar belakang dan sandaran untuk kawasan skin tertentu."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31922"
msgid "Enable or disable various skin features."
msgstr "Dayakan atau nyahdayakan pelbagai ciri skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31923"
msgid "Customise artwork and install supported artwork packs."
msgstr "Sesuaikan karya seni dan pasang pek karya seni yang disokong."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31924"
msgid "Install and configure supported addons."
msgstr "Pasang dan konfigurasi pengaya yang disokong."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31925"
msgid "Enable and disable library views. Disabling library views on low spec systems may improve performance."
msgstr "Dayakan dan nyahdayakan paparan perpustakaan. Menyahdayakan paparan perpustakaan pada sistem berspesifikasi rendah mungkin meningkatkan prestasi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31926"
msgid "Shows scroll letter when scrolling in library views."
msgstr "Menunjukkan huruf tatal semasa menatal dalam paparan perpustakaan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31927"
msgid "Shows the alphabet to jump to a position of the container. Will only work for default sorting methods (A-Z)."
msgstr "Menunjukkan abjad untuk melompat ke kedudukan bekas. Hanya berfungsi untuk kaedah pengisihan lalai (A-Z)."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31928"
msgid "Shows plot outline for tv shows and movies if available, otherwise will display the default plot."
msgstr "Menunjukkan garis plot untuk rancangan TV dan filem jika tersedia, jika tidak ia akan memaparkan plot lalai."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31929"
msgid "Auto scroll the plot if it does not fit the control dimensions."
msgstr "Skrin tatal plot secara automatik jika ia tidak sesuai dengan dimensi kawalan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31930"
msgid "Enable the shortcut menu for instant access to specific skin areas. In the media menu click left to open or click on the shortcut icon."
msgstr "Dayakan menu pintasan untuk akses segera ke kawasan skin tertentu. Dalam menu media klik kiri untuk membuka atau klik pada ikon pintasan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31931"
msgid "Edit the shortcut menu."
msgstr "Edit menu pintasan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31932"
msgid "Enable and disable the topbar elements."
msgstr "Dayakan dan nyahdayakan elemen bar atas."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31933"
msgid "Change video info settings."
msgstr "Tukar tetapan maklumat video."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31934"
msgid "Change music info settings."
msgstr "Tukar tetapan maklumat muzik."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31935"
msgid "Change fullscreen video settings."
msgstr "Tukar tetapan video skrin penuh."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31936"
msgid "Change fullscreen audio settings."
msgstr "Tukar tetapan audio skrin penuh."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31937"
msgid "Reduce the size of pop up notifications."
msgstr "Kurangkan saiz notifikasi timbul."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31938"
msgid "Darkens the screen behind dialog popups. Not applicable for fullscreen video or audio."
msgstr "Gelapkan skrin di belakang dialog timbul. Tidak terpakai untuk video atau audio skrin penuh."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31940"
msgid "Enable coloured icons for the topbar, media information and library views."
msgstr "Dayakan ikon berwarna untuk bar atas, maklumat media dan paparan perpustakaan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31941"
msgid "Enable coloured, HDR, bit depth and language media flags."
msgstr "Dayakan bendera media berwarna, HDR, kedalaman bit dan bahasa."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31943"
msgid "Audio cd art fallback skin wide."
msgstr "Sandaran seni CD audio untuk keseluruhan skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31944"
msgid "Video cd art fallback skin wide."
msgstr "Sandaran seni CD video untuk keseluruhan skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31945"
msgid "Select and install a weather icon pack for the topbar, widgets and weather."
msgstr "Pilih dan pasang pek ikon cuaca untuk bar atas, widget dan cuaca."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31946"
msgid "Select and install a weather fanart pack for the backgrounds, widgets and weather."
msgstr "Pilih dan pasang pek seni kipas cuaca untuk latar belakang, widget dan cuaca."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31947"
msgid "Install white studio icons for use throughout the skin."
msgstr "Pasang ikon studio putih untuk digunakan di seluruh skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31948"
msgid "Install coloured studio icons for use throughout the skin."
msgstr "Pasang ikon studio berwarna untuk digunakan di seluruh skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31949"
msgid "Install record label icons for use throughout the skin."
msgstr "Pasang ikon label rekod untuk digunakan di seluruh skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31950"
msgid "Install language flags for library views and subtitle selection."
msgstr "Pasang bendera bahasa untuk paparan perpustakaan dan pemilihan sarikata."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31951"
msgid "Install music genre icons for music and music videos."
msgstr "Pasang ikon genre muzik untuk muzik dan video muzik."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31952"
msgid "Install coloured movie genre icons for movies and tv shows."
msgstr "Pasang ikon genre filem berwarna untuk filem dan rancangan TV."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31953"
msgid "Install black and white movie genre icons for movies and tv shows."
msgstr "Pasang ikon genre filem hitam putih untuk filem dan rancangan TV."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31954"
msgid "Install country icons for movies country node."
msgstr "Pasang ikon negara untuk nod negara filem."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31955"
msgid "Set the delay between fanart transitions skin wide."
msgstr "Tetapkan kelengahan antara peralihan seni kipas untuk keseluruhan skin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31956"
msgid "Falling background effects. Snow, Leaves etc."
msgstr "Kesan latar belakang jatuh. Salji, Daun dll."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31957"
msgid "Show music fanart of currently playing item skin wide. Overrides library fanart."
msgstr "Tunjukkan seni kipas muzik bagi item yang sedang dimainkan untuk keseluruhan skin. Mengatasi seni kipas perpustakaan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31958"
msgid "Enables music visualisation in background while playing music. Requires visualisation to be enabled in settings - Player settings/Music."
msgstr "Membolehkan visualisasi muzik di latar belakang semasa memainkan muzik. Memerlukan visualisasi didayakan dalam tetapan - Tetapan pemain/Muzik."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31959"
msgid "Show now playing video in background while browsing library. Overrides library fanart."
msgstr "Tunjukkan video sedang dimainkan di latar belakang semasa melayari perpustakaan. Mengatasi seni kipas perpustakaan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31960"
msgid "Download images and additional information from fanart.tv and theaudiodb.com of the currently playing artist. For fullscreen music, internet streams and radio."
msgstr "Muat turun imej dan maklumat tambahan daripada fanart.tv dan theaudiodb.com bagi artis yang sedang dimainkan. Untuk muzik skrin penuh, aliran internet dan radio."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31962"
msgid "Artist slideshow script settings."
msgstr "Tetapan skrip slaid artis."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31963"
msgid "A shortcut to the video playlist if not empty."
msgstr "Pintasan ke senarai main video jika tidak kosong."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31964"
msgid "A shortcut to the music playlist if not empty."
msgstr "Pintasan ke senarai main muzik jika tidak kosong."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31965"
msgid "Shortcut to fullscreen when media is playing."
msgstr "Pintasan ke skrin penuh apabila media sedang dimainkan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31966"
msgid "Click to open shortcut menu."
msgstr "Klik untuk membuka menu pintasan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31967"
msgid "Player controls when media is playing."
msgstr "Kawalan pemain apabila media sedang dimainkan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31968"
msgid "Play the next TV show episode automatically."
msgstr "Mainkan episod rancangan TV seterusnya secara automatik."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31969"
msgid "Play themes while navigating TV Shows, Movies and Music Videos."
msgstr "Mainkan tema semasa menavigasi Rancangan TV, Filem dan Video Muzik."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31970"
msgid "The Library Node Editor allows you to create and customise custom video nodes and music nodes within Kodi."
msgstr "Library Node Editor membolehkan anda mencipta dan menyesuaikan nod video dan nod muzik tersuai di dalam Kodi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31971"
msgid "Show overlay marker information for watched, unwatched, and in progress media items."
msgstr "Tunjukkan maklumat penanda tindihan untuk item media yang ditonton, belum ditonton dan sedang berjalan."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31972"
msgid "A script for editing Kodi's built in RSS Ticker."
msgstr "Skrip untuk mengedit Ticker RSS terbina dalam Kodi."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31973"
msgid "Skin version and recovery options. Restores all defaults to day one operation."
msgstr "Versi skin dan pilihan pemulihan. Memulihkan semua lalai kepada operasi hari pertama."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31974"
msgid "Addons"
msgstr "Pengaya"